                    <span>Joe Sugarman has been in marketing for many years. In Triggers he gives specific examples of marketing tools to use including explaining why your product is better over all as well as a lower price than a competing product.<br>He also gives information on how to become a better buyer by looking at different factors when you want to make a purchase. His writing is light, fun, and informational.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">How to get more sales starting today!</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
